Airline Data

completeFun <- function(data, desiredCols) {
  completeVec <- complete.cases(data[, desiredCols])
  return(data[completeVec,])
}

subset_analysis <- completeFun(subset, "airplane_model")
subset_analysis <-
subset(subset_analysis, select = c("airplane_model", "DepDelay"))
subset_analysis <- completeFun(subset_analysis, "DepDelay")
df <- group_by(subset_analysis, airplane_model) %>%
filter(n() > 50)
df$delay <- df$DepDelay > 0
df2 <- group_by(df, airplane_model, delay) %>%
summarise(n())
df2["delay_percentage"] <- NA
colnames(df2)[3] <- "count"
for (i in 1:nrow(df2) - 1) {
df2[i, ]$delay_percentage <-
df2[i + 1, ]$count / (df2[i + 1, ]$count + df2[i, ]$count)
}
toDelete <- seq(0, nrow(df2), 2)
df2 <- df2[-toDelete,]
final <-
select(arrange(df2, desc(delay_percentage)), airplane_model, delay_percentage)
final
